<paragraph blockId="7.[151,1437,1225,1538]" pageId="7" pageNumber="158">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,308,1441,1466]" pageId="7" pageNumber="158">Remarks</emphasis>
. This species is widely distributed in 
<collectingCountry box="[759,827,1441,1466]" name="Brazil" pageId="7" pageNumber="158">Brazil</collectingCountry>
and in the Northeast Region, having been recorded previously only from 
<collectingRegion box="[395,460,1477,1502]" country="Brazil" name="Bahia" pageId="7" pageNumber="158">Bahia</collectingRegion>
State. In this study the known distribution is extended and provides the first record for the state of 
<collectingRegion box="[281,395,1513,1538]" country="Brazil" name="Maranhao" pageId="7" pageNumber="158">Maranhão</collectingRegion>
[Caxias Municipality].
</paragraph>
